# Naming Conventions

## Python Backend

```python
# Classes: PascalCase
class EasyPostService:
    pass

class ShipmentResponse:
    pass

# Functions/Methods: snake_case
def create_shipment():
    pass

async def get_tracking():
    pass

# Constants: UPPER_SNAKE_CASE
MAX_FILE_SIZE = 10 * 1024 * 1024
DEFAULT_TIMEOUT = 30

# Private methods: _leading_underscore
def _create_shipment_sync():
    pass

# Files: snake_case
easypost_service.py
shipment_tools.py
```

## React Frontend

```javascript
// Components: PascalCase, .jsx extension
Dashboard.jsx
ShipmentForm.jsx
TrackingList.jsx

// Functions/Hooks: camelCase
function handleCreateShipment() {}
function useShipment() {}

// Constants: UPPER_SNAKE_CASE
const API_URL = 'http://localhost:8000/mcp';
const DEFAULT_TIMEOUT = 30000;

// Files:
// - Components: PascalCase.jsx
// - Utils: camelCase.js
// - Styles: PascalCase.css
Dashboard.jsx
Dashboard.css
apiService.js
```

## Quick Reference

| Element | Convention | Example |
|---------|-----------|---------|
| Python Functions | snake_case | `create_shipment()` |
| Python Classes | PascalCase | `EasyPostService` |
| Python Constants | UPPER_SNAKE_CASE | `MAX_SIZE` |
| React Components | PascalCase.jsx | `Dashboard.jsx` |
| React Functions | camelCase | `handleClick()` |
| React Constants | UPPER_SNAKE_CASE | `API_URL` |
